name: src/index.js
content:
export * from './tools' ;
export * from './formats' ;

name: src/tools/chain.js
chain
description: Converts a stream of streams of tokens to a stream of tokens.

name: src/tools/exhaust.js
exhaust
description: Exhausts a stream.

name: src/tools/from/from.js
fromiterable
description: Converts an iterable to a stream.

name: fromiterator
description: Converts an iterator to a stream.

name: fromcallable
description: Converts a callable to a stream.

name: StreamFromCallable
description: Class that wraps a callable with a stream.

name: constructor
description: The constructor. Stores the callable that yields values to stream.

name: read
description: Returns the next token in the stream.

name: unread
description:
Puts a token back in the stream. If {@link StreamFromCallable#read} is
used just after, this token will be returned.

params.name: token
params.description: The token to put back in the stream.

name: fromstring
description: Converts a string to a stream.

name: fromarray
description: Converts an array to a stream.

name: src/tools/from/index.js
content: export * from './from' ;

name: src/tools/ignore.js
ignore
description: Filters a stream by ignoring a given set of tokens.

name: src/tools/index.js
src/tools/map.js
map
description: Applies a callable to each token of a stream.

name: src/tools/skip/index.js
content: export * from './skip' ;

name: src/tools/skip/skip.js
skip
description:
Outputs the next token of a stream that is not contained in a given toskip
set.

name: src/tools/split/index.js
content: export * from './split' ;

name: src/tools/split/split.js
split
description:
Splits the input stream into a stream of streams according to some set of
separators. See {@link _split} for the actual implementation.

name: _split
description: Same as {@link split}, but returns an iterator rather than a stream.

name: src/tools/to/index.js
src/tools/to/toarray.js
toarray
description: Converts a stream to an array.

name: src/tools/to/toiterable.js
toiterable
description: Converts a stream to an iterable.

name: src/tools/to/toiterator.js
toiterator
description: Converts a stream to an iterator.

name: src/tools/to/tostring.js
tostring
description: Converts a stream to a string.
